request_text: show complaint counts by product and state for the last 12 months

policy_decision.reason: Low sensitivity data allowed for all authenticated roles

sql.final_sql: SELECT state, product, COUNT(*) AS complaint_count FROM dp_complaints WHERE 1=1 AND date_received >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '12 months' GROUP BY state, product HAVING COUNT(*) >= 10 ORDER BY state
sql.canonical_sql: SELECT STATE, PRODUCT, COUNT(*) AS COMPLAINT_COUNT FROM DP_COMPLAINTS WHERE 1=1 AND DATE_RECEIVED >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '12 MONTHS' GROUP BY STATE, PRODUCT HAVING COUNT(*) >= 10 ORDER BY STATE
